  <brief_title>Exercise as a Life-long Medicine in Patients With Coronary Artery Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>How to Enhance Physical Activity After Cardiac Rehabilitation? A Randomised Controlled Study Comparing Two Follow-up Training Exercise Programs</official_title>
